text: Google fans have probably been ecstatic this week because they favorite company has recently unveiled not one, but two Nexus devices, the Nexus 5X and Nexus 6P . While the two phones can’t be considered such a major upgrade compared to last year’s devices, they still come with some nifty additions like fingerprint scanners and reversible USB Type-C ports.
